This directory contains MMSP code for grain growth simulations using the Monte Carlo method that come from the cited below.

Send questions or comments to tany3@rpi.edu (Yixuan Tan)

References:

1. Wright, Steven A., et al. "Potts-model grain growth simulations: Parallel algorithms and applications." SAND Report (1997): 1925.
2. Godfrey, A. W., and J. W. Martin. "Some Monte Carlo studies of grain growth in a temperature gradient." Philosophical Magazine A 72.3 (1995): 737-749.
